    Content-Type: application/json - Indicates the media type (MIME type) for the request body. Chatbot APIs only support media type application/json.
    cnx-correlationId: Unique ID that is used to track API calls made in the same session. It is recommended that, as an API consumer, you assign a new correlation ID for the first API call in a session and use the same ID for all subsequent APIs. If you encounter any issue in your API calls, you must provide this ID to our support executive.
