    cnx-userip: IP address of the customer. The customer is the end-user who is making the booking. 
    Ensure that your integration passes the customer's IP address instead of your own IP address. The customer's IP address helps determine their location and assigns the correct payment gateway. The IP address can also be used for fraud recovery and other analytics.
